<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>오늘의 가계부</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/reset.css" />

    <style>
      @import url(http://fonts.googleapis.com/earlyaccess/notosanskr.css);

      @media (max-width: 996px) {
        html {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        img {
          display: none;
        }
        .title {
          font-size: 2rem !important;
        }

        .catchphrase {
          font-size: 1.3rem !important;
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          margin-left: 1.5rem !important;
        }

        .catchphrase p {
          padding-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .container_right {
          width: 52vw !important;
        }

        .body_bg {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 680px) {
        html {
          font-size: 12px;
        }
        .button {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }

        .yes,
        .no {
          margin: 2em !important;
        }

        .yes {
          margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
        }

        .no {
          margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
        }

        button {
          width: 14rem !important;
          line-height: 1rem !important;
        }

        .title,
        .catchphrase {
          margin: 0 auto !important;
          margin-bottom: 1.5rem !important;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 567px) {
        .button {
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          flex-direction: column;
        }
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 375px) {
        .button {
          margin-top: 2rem !important;
        }
      }

      /* --------------------------------------------------------------------- */
      .body_bg {
        background-color: rgb(55, 132, 255);
      }

      .box {
        font-family: "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        margin: 100px 0px;
      }

      .container {
        width: 80vw;
        height: 70vh;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background-color: rgb(255, 221, 239);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-evenly;
        align-items: center;
      }

      img {
        width: 35vw;
        height: 50vh;
        border-radius: 15px;
        margin: 10px;
      }

      .container_right {
        width: 35vw;
        height: 50vh;
        margin: 30px;
      }

      .title {
        margin: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 4.5vw;
      }

      .catchphrase {
        margin: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0;
        height: 20vh;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
        color: black;
      }

      .button_box {
        height: 10vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      button {
        width: 8rem;
        line-height: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        border: none;
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        font-family: "paybooc-Light", sans-serif;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: 0.25s;
        background-color: #6fb1b4;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .yes {
        margin: 20px;
      }
      .no {
        margin: 20px;
      }

      .yes:hover {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        transform: scale(1.2);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .no:hover {
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        transform: scale(1.2);
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body class="body_bg">
    <!-- tutorial -->
    <div class="box">
      <div class="container">
        <img src="/static/img/pig_tutorial.jpg" alt="pig_tutorial" />

        <div class="container_right">
          <div class="title">
            <p>오늘의 가계부</p>
          </div>

          <div class="catchphrase">
            <p>1인 가구를 위한 간단한 기능부터 생활 꿀팁까지!</p>
            <p>오늘부터 가계부 작성하시고 알뜰한 삶을 얻어보세요👍</p>
            <p>저희 서비스를 이용한 경험이 있으신가요?</p>
          </div>

          <div class="button_box">
            <div class="button">
              <!-- 캘린더 페이지로 이동 -->
              <button
                type="button"
                class="yes"
                onclick="location.href='/main?category=카페'"
                ;
              >
                Yes
              </button>

              <!-- 소비성향 테스트로 이동 -->
              <button
                type="button"
                class="no"
                onclick="location.href='tutorial2'"
                ;
              >
                No
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
